@host = http://localhost:4000
@scenarioVersion = {{$timestamp}}

### Leitura antes de qualquer configuração (200, whatsappNumber: null) — sem JWT, rota pública
GET {{host}}/settings

### Cadastrar usuário "owner" para autenticar (201)
# @name registerOwner
POST {{host}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin Owner",
  "email": "owner-settings-{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Login para obter token (200)
# @name loginOwner
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "owner-settings-{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

###
@token = {{loginOwner.response.body.token}}

### Atualizar sem JWT é bloqueado (401)
PUT {{host}}/settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "whatsappNumber": "+5511999998888"
}

### Atualizar configuração (204) — cria o registro único na primeira chamada
PUT {{host}}/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "whatsappNumber": "+5511999998888"
}

### Leitura após configurar (200, whatsappNumber preenchido) — continua pública
GET {{host}}/settings

### Atualizar novamente (204) — mesma chamada atualiza o registro existente
PUT {{host}}/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "whatsappNumber": "+5511888887777"
}

### Atualizar com número inválido (422, errors[] inclui settings.whatsappNumber.phone)
PUT {{host}}/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "whatsappNumber": "11999998888"
}

### Upload de logo sem JWT é bloqueado (401)
POST {{host}}/settings/logo
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary--

### Upload de logo (201, retorna { logoUrl } absoluta)
POST {{host}}/settings/logo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="logo.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./product-image-sample.png
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### Leitura reflete a logo configurada (200, logoUrl preenchida)
GET {{host}}/settings

### Remover logo sem JWT é bloqueado (401)
DELETE {{host}}/settings/logo

### Remover logo (204)
DELETE {{host}}/settings/logo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Leitura após remover (200, logoUrl: null)
GET {{host}}/settings
